com.hazelcast.client.impl.protocol

Class ResponseMessageConst

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.client.impl.protocol.ResponseMessageConst

  • public final class ResponseMessageConst
extends Object
    Message type ids of responses in client protocol. They also used to bind a request to a response inside Request annotation.

    Response classes are defined com.hazelcast.client.impl.protocol.template.ResponseTemplate

    see com.hazelcast.client.impl.protocol.template.ClientMessageTemplate#addMembershipListener(boolean) ()} for a sample usage of responses in a request.
